title: Issue running jasmine tests. Getting TypeError: instanceof called on an object with an invalid prototype property
body:
Hi, new to react. So, maybe I'm missing something obvious. I'm using the following relevant node modules:
- "gulp-karma": "0.0.4",
- "karma-react-jsx-preprocessor": "^0.1.0",
- "karma-jasmine": "^0.2.2",
- "karma": "^0.12.9"

I'm using the following bower dependencies:
- "react": "~0.10.0",
- "bind-polyfill": "*", // this is to polyfill PhantomJS .bind() method

Here is my test file: https://gist.github.com/awei01/11159942

I'm getting this stack trace:
